{
  "stem": "12666.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even we had some napkins with the Nazi insignia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That disappeared, too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We got paper napkins after it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Everybody was taking souvenirs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I guess that's one of our national sports, right, take some souvenirs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them were discharged from the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were some army personnel too, like Colonel Dostert.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in charge of the interpreters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was the one that introduced that simultaneous translation that is being used at the UN.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He introduced that, where you had a dial and you could have simultaneous translation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That is a contribution to Nuremberg trial, to our country here, because I understand Georgetown University is using the same method too, you know, with-- which Colonel Dostert introduced in Georgetown after the Nuremberg trial.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was a gift of the Nuremberg trial to the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had very nice quarters and were very well taken care of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the only thing is that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the beginning, it was very hard to read those documents that we captured.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was very hard to read those documents, because the Germans are very thorough and they go into details.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were not-- they didn't take any effort to destroy the evidence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the evidence was there, snapshots, everything described in detail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of those crimes are not even mentioned today, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like for example, making soap out of human bodies, or lampshades were made.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went into detail describing everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even their testimony-- some people were even proud of committing horrible war crimes, like the commander of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw him for two days.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
